                            Process Refund
                        </DialogTitle>
                        <DialogDescription className="text-slate-500 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
                            Are you sure you want to refund this transaction? The exact amount will be credited back to the user's secure wallet.
                        </DialogDescription>
                    </DialogHeader>
                    <div className="space-y-4">
                        <div className="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 p-4 rounded-xl flex flex-col gap-2">
